    <voice name="zh-CN-XiaohanNeural">
        <mstts:express-as style="cheerful">”等着，咱们两个一起走，
            <prosody rate="+5.00%" pitch="+6.00%">瞧瞧</prosody>
            <prosody contour="(49%, -11%)">他</prosody>
            <prosody rate="+6.00%">
                <phoneme alphabet="sapi" ph="qu 5">去</phoneme>
            </prosody>
            。”
        </mstts:express-as>
    </voice>
    <voice name="zh-CN-YunxiNeural">
        <mstts:express-as style="Calm">“好好的<prosody pitch="+4.00%">又</prosody>生气了！就是我说错了，你到底也还<prosody
